{"post_stream":{"posts":[{"id":3153122,"name":"Josh","username":"Skyhawk246","avatar_template":"/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/s/67e7ee/{size}.png","created_at":"2023-02-26T16:19:08.915Z","cooked":"<p>our team has been experiencing an issue with implementing the spark max code, the code will compile but sends error 4 &amp; 5 to the Roborio. The code however will enable but will also send the error message error 4. Here’s our code</p>
<p>// Copyright (c) FIRST and other WPILib contributors.<br>
